                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <div id="idZone" style="color: green; font-size: 20px; margin-top: 20px"></div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <h6 class="mt-2 text-primary text-center font-20">비밀번호를 잊어버리셨나요?</h6>
                        <div class="form-1" style="margin-bottom: 50px">
                            <p class="text-center text-muted mt-3 mb-3 font-14">아이디와 E-mail주소를 입력하세요</p>
                            <h6 class="mt-4 text-primary  font-20">아이디</h6>
                            <div class="login-one-inputs">
                                <input type="text" id="memId" placeholder="아이디를 입력하세요"/>
                                <i class="las la-envelope"></i> 
                            </div>
                            <h6 class="mt-2 text-primary  font-20">이메일</h6>
                            <div class="login-one-inputs mt-3">
                                <input type="text" id="memMail2" placeholder="이메일을 입력하세요"/>
                                <i class="las la-envelope"></i> 
                            </div>
